{
  "stem": "11552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when my mother and some of the people went into that barn, in two barns, I was afraid to go into the barn because I was afraid they will come after us, you know, I was already so fright.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a dog house there, and I climbed-- crawled into that dog house, and I stayed in the dog house, looking out, hope if something will happen so I can go and protect them again.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the farmer came out, and he wanted his dog to go into dog house, and the dog was barking because he couldn't go into the dog house because I was in the dog house.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The poor dog got such a very bad time, he couldn't go in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I felt badly for the dog.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, that's the time when I stopped sleeping nights, because I was constantly watching and being afraid that they may come back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, that was-- Where would you be sleeping?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would not be-- We-- we had to go back to Wojciu.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had absolutely nowhere to be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were just waiting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had nowhere to go, because we couldn't be in the barns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They found out, they would kill us there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went back to Wojciu.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we-- we went back, I went, during the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was trying to beg for some food and some work, but at night-- I knew they would come, if they come, at night-- I was on watch.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought hopefully that I will be awake, and I will be able to stop them from killing us the second time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they never came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
